DDEESSCCRRIIPPTTIIOONN
     This manual page documents the GNU version of llss.  ddiirr and vvddiirr are
     versions of llss with different default output formats.   These  pro-
     grams  list  each given file or directory path.  Directory contents
     are sorted alphabetically.  For llss, files are by default listed  in
     columns,  sorted  vertically, if the standard output is a terminal;
     otherwise they are listed one per line.  For ddiirr, files are by  de-
     fault listed in columns, sorted vertically.  For vvddiirr, files are by
     default listed in long format.

